*===========================================================
*   N A M E   V A R I A N T   O V E R R I D E   T A B L E
*===========================================================
* 1st Column = Variant Group
* Subsequent Columns: Variants (up to 64)
* Maximum column width = 16
* At least 2 spaces or <tab> between columns
* Variants are automatically cross-referenced to the group
*   unless another group entry is defined for a variant
*   or it already exists in the system-table with variants
*-----------------------------------------------------------

